originalText.text: Dr. Ottono Usanga was one of the best doctors I’ve seen. He was very thorough and explained everything about my annual. He was also able to help me with my blocked ear. I was so miserable but after applying his suggestion I feel so much better and it’s only been a day! I wish he could be my new primary doctor as I’m my previous one left.
